## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="328a4-268"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> admite conversiones implícitas de las clases siguientes:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="328a4-268"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> supports implicit conversions from the following classes:</span></span>  
  
