-   <span data-ttu-id="328a4-416">fr-FR.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="328a4-416">fr-FR.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="328a4-417">Francés (Francia)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="328a4-417">French (France)</span></span>  
  
